OL,3,CWhat is an 'orderly' replacement of
OL,4,CStarmer?
OL,6,FMost of us don't need to consult an AI
OL,7,Fsuper-brain to attach the appropriate
OL,8,Fprobability to ministerial turkeys
OL,9,Fvoting for Christmas.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FSo tomorrow's 49th relaunch speech by
OL,17,Fthe PM is both profoundly important
OL,18,Fand trivially unimportant.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
